description:
This is a 60 minute workout called 'Enter a Deep Sleep while Connecting to your Higher Self (Guided Meditation)' from the channel Great Meditation.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Sleep Prep vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This one-hour deep sleep guided meditation is designed to offer a profound journey allowing you to release the stresses of the day and embrace a serene connection with your higher self.  As the soothing voice gently guides you, you'll embark on a transformative exploration of your inner world.  This meditation aims to create a sacred space for introspection, promoting a sense of inner peace and rejuvenation.  By immersing yourself in this profound sleep meditation, you open the door to self-discovery, inviting the wisdom of your higher self to guide you through a restful night's sleep, fostering a deeper connection with your innermost essence.  Embrace this opportunity to embark on a journey of inner alignment and renewal, as you gracefully surrender to the restorative power of sleep and higher self connection.
This is an Original guided meditation recorded by us.
